node.text:
In your shelter I stay, in your hands you keep me. 
There’s no fear when you are with me. In your shelter I stay, in your hands you keep me.

The storm came in, we searched for safety 
I surrendered there, in your arms you held me
Cause the waves were high, but your wings were greater. 
Lifted up, I abide.
When I met you there in the secret place 
A place I always feel safe.

There’s no fear in love, perfect peace surrounds me. No fear in love, perfect peace surrounds me. Lifted up, I abide.
